			<header>Scientific Method: Experiment</header>
			<instruction>Gathering Data: Independent Variable</instruction>
		</content>
		<activity type="image">
			<image>psy_m3-1_s8.jpg</image>
			<hotspots>
				<hotspot title="Experimental Group" audio="psy_m3-1_s8_a" dynamic="true" x="34" y="148">
					<![CDATA[
					<h1>Experimental Group</h1>
					<p>The experimental group experiences the independent variable.</p>
					]]>
				</hotspot>
				<hotspot title="Independent Variable" audio="psy_m3-1_s8_b" dynamic="true" x="410" y="10">
					<![CDATA[
					<h1>Independent Variable</h1>
					<p>The independent variable is the factor that is being changed or manipulated. The researcher manipulates the independent variable.</p>
					]]>
				</hotspot>
				<hotspot title="Control Group" audio="psy_m3-1_s8_c" dynamic="true" x="473" y="187">
					<![CDATA[
					<h1>Control Group</h1>
					<p>The control group does not receive the independent variable.</p>
					]]>
				</hotspot>
				<hotspot title="Researcher" audio="psy_m3-1_s8_d" dynamic="true" x="318" y="147">
					<![CDATA[
					<h1>Researcher</h1>
					<p>Example: the researcher wants to know if the subject will steal if alone. The independent variable is whether the subject is alone.</p>
					]]>
				</hotspot>
			</hotspots>
		</activity>
